Sized to fit over a standard wetsuit, the Spearfishing Camouflage shirt and pants negate the necessity to purchase a separate spearfishing wetsuit. Brown abstract camouflage mirrors the underwater environment for excellent disguise. Smooth Lycra Spandex material sheds water easily, and comes with a built-in chest loading pad.

Material Structure
  • Highest quality 5.5oz Spandex material
  • Provides protection against UV rays
Construction
  • Flat-stitched throughout entire suit
Extra Features
  • Stirrup for feet
  • Hood and waist drawstring
  • Chest loading pad
Note: Sizing based on fit over wetsuit. When worn alone, go one size down.

Description:
The embodiment of style and utility, the Zenith 3/2mm Supreme Stretch D-Zip Full Suit from the Tilos 2010 Line epitomizes the luxurious comfort modern divers aught to enjoy with current diving technologies. The top-of-the-line suit design is based on 250% Supreme Stretch fabric throughout for maximum warmth and movement, and topped off with numerous features that excel over all other competition.

Material Structure

  • 250% SupremeStretch material double-lined throughout entire suit
  • 3mm Thermowall body - enhanced heat retention & quick-dry feature
  • 9mm thick Deluxe Hydroplane Foam spine pad seals water entrance and cushions back
  • 2mm sleeves & lower legs
  • 1mm Glidskin in inner wrists/cuffs

Construction

  • Quadruple watertight glued throughout entire suit
  • Blindstitched inside & outside entire suit

Extra Features

  • SupremeStretch fabric molds to individual body shapes like a second skin
  • Back water barrier YKK #10 metal zipper
  • Water barrier YKK #5 front zipper
  • Water barrier YKK #10 wrist & ankle zippers
  • Prebent Tatex kneepads
Name: 3/2MM ZENITH SUPREME STRETCH D-ZIP FULL (Male)
